01:56:16.440 --> 01:56:18.440
And how was I supposed to know that?

01:56:18.440 --> 01:56:20.440
We better get them before they get us,

01:56:20.440 --> 01:56:22.440
Day-day.

01:56:22.440 --> 01:56:24.440
Ooh, I'm so scared.

01:56:24.440 --> 01:56:26.440
Alright, I made a mistake.

01:56:26.440 --> 01:56:28.440
I never thought you'd forget this.

01:56:28.440 --> 01:56:30.440
Oh, give me a break.

01:56:30.440 --> 01:56:32.440
You're a loser.

01:56:32.440 --> 01:56:34.440
You're a big loser.

01:56:34.440 --> 01:56:38.580
They were in here, weren't they?

01:56:38.580 --> 01:56:40.580
I'm afraid so.

01:56:40.580 --> 01:56:42.580
No matter.

01:56:42.580 --> 01:56:44.580
Tonight's the night.

01:56:46.580 --> 01:57:13.970
You feel better soon, master.

01:57:13.970 --> 01:57:16.970
You've been invited in by new victims.

01:57:16.970 --> 01:57:20.970
You are wise in coming to this country.

01:57:20.970 --> 01:57:23.970
There is so much more fresh blood here.

01:57:24.970 --> 01:57:28.970
And no one believes that the little boy can be a vampire.

01:57:34.970 --> 01:57:45.220
With ghosts and ghouls, there are no rules.

01:57:45.220 --> 01:57:50.220
But a vampire's bite only comes at night.

01:57:50.220 --> 01:58:00.320
I declare this meeting of the Midnight Society closed.

01:58:00.320 --> 01:58:04.590
Until next time.

01:58:04.590 --> 01:58:10.140
Pleasant dreams, everyone.

